import React from 'react';
import { Container, Form, Button } from 'react-bootstrap';

const Input = ({}) => (
    <Form className='container col-sm-6 mt-5'>
        <Form.Group>
            <Form.Control 
                type='text' 
                placeholder='Type a message...'
            />
        </Form.Group>
        <Form.Group>
        <Button variant="primary" type="submit">
                Submit
        </Button>
        </Form.Group>
    </Form>
    
   
)

export default Input;
